summary:
Started playing this adorable game, and I was surprised at how much I like it! 💙

I probably never would have picked up Pokémon:...
caption:
Started playing this adorable game, and I was surprised at how much I like it! 💙

I probably never would have picked up Pokémon: Let’s Go, Eevee! on my own since I didn’t have much interest in it when it came out (so thank you, @ibenlo for the wonderful birthday gift!).

It’s cute as heck, nostalgic, and fun, and really this post was a huge excuse to have a tiny photography session with my Eevee plush. Their name is Toast. 💙

summary: Baby Pichu! Based the little dude on an AU in which my OC Estelle and Meowth get their hands on an egg and end up raising the...
body:
Baby Pichu! Based the little dude on an AU in which my OC Estelle and Meowth get their hands on an egg and end up raising the baby in shared custody (as friends ofc)

Basically like Togepi but Meowth gets to be the dad we know he can be.

And the egg turning out to be a Pichu just felt like an ironic twist lmao
